*根因**: Redis存储层性能问题（rrt_max）\n- **直接受害者**: CartService（依赖redis）\n- **间接受害者**: CheckoutService（依赖CartService）\n- **最终影响**: Frontend用户体验\n\n### 故障影响范围\n- **主要影响**: 购物车和结算流程\n- **次要影响**: 产品目录和推荐服务（存在轻微延迟增加）\n- **时间窗口**: 17分钟的故障持续时间\n\n故障的根本原因是Redis存储层的严重性能退化，导致整个购物车和结算链路出现级联延迟。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "aiops-k8s-08 is the root cause due to node_filesystem_usage_rate exhaustion and node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes depletion"}
