常时段降至61546ms，可能发生快速失败或熔断\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析要点\n\n### 关键发现\n1. **CartService严重延迟**: cartservice的GetCart操作在异常时段响应时间从2.5秒飙升至23秒，延迟增加近9倍\n2. **Redis存储层问题**: redis的HGET操作延迟从1.5秒增加到14.8秒，表明存储层存在严重性能问题\n3. **CheckoutService异常**: PlaceOrder操作响应时间异常下降，可能发生了快速失败或熔断机制触发\n\n### 根因分析\n根据调用拓扑和延迟分析，故障传播路径为：\n- **根因**: Redis存储层性能问题（rrt_max）\n- **直接受害者**: CartService（依赖redis）\n- **间接受害者**: CheckoutService（依赖CartService）\n- **最终影响**: Frontend用户体验\n\n### 故障影响范围\n- **主要影响**: 购物车和结算流程\n- **次要影响**: 产品目录和推荐服务（存在轻微延迟增加）\n- **时间窗口**: 17分钟的故障持续时间\n\n故障的根本原因是Redis存储层的严重性能退化，导致整个购物车和结算链路出现级联延迟。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "cc8e0450-593", "component": "aiops-k8s-08", "reason": "node_filesystem_usage_rate spike (53%→78%) and node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes drop (9.9GB→6.6GB) causing resource exhaustion", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(aiops-k8s-08)", "observation": "node_filesystem_usage_rate increased from 53.2% to 78.16%, node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes dropped 39.57%"}, {"step": 2, "action": "CheckNodePodMapping()", "observation": "redis-cart-0 and productcatalogservice-0 running on aiops-k8s-08"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(cc8e0450-593)", "observation": "redis-cart latency spike correlates with node resource pressure"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
